OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FFoyle Women's Aid have said they have
OL,7,Freceived an unprecedented number of
OL,8,Fcalls following the murder of Amy
OL,9,FDoherty in Londonderry.
OL,11,FThe charity's chief executive was
OL,12,Fspeaking at the launch of a new
OL,13,Finitiative spearheaded by teenagers in
OL,14,Fthe city, aimed at raising awareness
OL,15,Fof domestic abuse.
OL,17,FMarie Brown said: "There has been a
OL,18,Fwave of people just calling for a
OL,19,Frange of things.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
