PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,F"The phones haven't stopped and it is
OL,7,Fall women who are in situations who
OL,8,Fsay, 'I need to come forward now after
OL,9,Frecognising the risks'."
OL,11,FThe murder of Amy Doherty in Derry
OL,12,Fhappened earlier this month.
OL,14,FAddressing the crowd at a vigil in
OL,15,Fmemory of the mother-of-two on Friday
OL,16,Fat the Guildhall, Amy's mother Sharon
OL,17,Fsaid her daughter's death must not be
OL,18,Fin vain.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
