OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, students launched a book
OL,7,Fat the Guildhall, designed to raise
OL,8,Fawareness of domestic abuse among
OL,9,Fyoung people.
OL,11,FSix thousand copies were printed,
OL,12,Favailable for distribution in local
OL,13,Fschools and youth clubs.
OL,15,FThe content was also dramatised at the
OL,16,Flaunch, in a play highlighting the
OL,17,Fdangers of coercive control.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
