PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FIt is part of a number of innovative
OL,7,Fapproaches deployed in the area to
OL,8,Freduce the harm faced by women and
OL,9,Fgirls.
OL,11,FThe book has been developed by pupils
OL,12,Ffrom a number of different schools
OL,13,Facross the Derry City & Strabane
OL,14,Fdistrict Council area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
