FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FIt tells the story of two young
OL,7,Fpeople, both fictional characters, who
OL,8,Fexperience domestic abuse - physical,
OL,9,Fverbal, psychological, emotional and
OL,10,Fsexual violence ` in their
OL,11,Frelationships, and how, with the help
OL,12,Fof family, friends, and police, they
OL,13,Fare supported and helped.
OL,15,FTeenagers aged between 14 and 17
OL,16,Fworked through a series of evening
OL,17,Fworkshops to develop the storyline and
OL,18,Fdesign the comic book.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
