SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FYear 10 students from St Cecilia's
OL,7,FCollege in Derry were among those to
OL,8,Ftake part in the project.
OL,10,FCasey Young said: "Even if this can
OL,11,Fstop one abuser from forming or show
OL,12,Fsomeone that you're not alone and you
OL,13,Fcan get help as well, that would mean
OL,14,Fso much to me, and I'd be so proud to
OL,15,Fsay I've done this."
OL,17,FOne of the students involved said the
OL,18,Fbook "uses modern language for younger
OL,19,Freaders to help them understand and
OL,20,Frelate to the themes within, and is
OL,21,Fsomething a lot of people go through".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,FAnother student said they "learned
OL,7,Fabout who to go to about (domestic)
OL,8,Fviolence and what to do in that
OL,9,Fsituation and I think it's a good
OL,10,Fmessage to share in schools".
OL,12,FAnother added: "This comic book really
OL,13,Fhighlights the stuff we need to talk
OL,14,Fabout."
OL,16,FDerry City & Strabane PSNI Chief
OL,17,FInspector Cherith Craig was also
OL,18,Finvolved in the project.JShe said:
OL,19,F"Working with these incredibly
OL,20,Ftalented and vibrant young minds has
OL,21,Fbeen an amazing experience."
OL,26,@oD@ZpmoD@cpntD@POUvD@GO]{D@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
