OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775052666
OL,3,CFoyle Women's Aid receives increased
OL,4,Ccalls following Amy Doherty's murder
OL,6,F"They've developed a story about
OL,7,Fdomestic abuse and how it impacts
OL,8,Fpeople their age, which is why it was
OL,9,Fso important the story is told the way
OL,10,Fthey want it."
OL,12,FThe event was attended by Justice
OL,13,FMinister Naomi Long ahead of a meeting
OL,14,Fwith Amy Doherty's parents.
OL,16,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,17,Faddressed the audience by video and
OL,18,FSecretary of State Hilary Benn also
OL,19,Fattended.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
